WEBVTT

00:02:29.127 --> 00:02:32.518
picha ndogo zisizo na rangi zilizochoka

00:02:32.542 --> 00:02:34.746
za marafiki zake wapya wa kigeni.

00:02:36.387 --> 00:02:40.014
Hivyo tulivyoagana usiku ule,

00:02:40.038 --> 00:02:42.625
nikagundua kua amenionyesha pia

00:02:42.649 --> 00:02:44.959
siri ya kwenye kusafiri,

00:02:44.983 --> 00:02:47.039
ambayo ni kufanya kitu bila uwoga,

00:02:47.063 --> 00:02:49.755
kusafiri ndani vile vile na nje,

00:02:49.779 --> 00:02:52.294
kwenda sehemu ambazo usingeenda
vinginevyo,

00:02:52.990 --> 00:02:55.498
kufanya usiyoyafahamu,

00:02:55.928 --> 00:02:57.101
usichokielewa,

00:02:57.498 --> 00:02:58.780
hata uwoga.